trans-unit.source: Retrieves values, as specified in a declarative expression, from the <xref uid="langword_csharp_<appSettings>" name="<appSettings>" href=""></xref> section of the Web.config file.
trans-unit.target: Henter verdier, som er angitt i et deklarerende uttrykk fra den <xref uid="langword_csharp_<appSettings>" name="<appSettings>" href=""> </xref> -delen i Web.config-filen.

trans-unit.source: The AppSettingsExpressionBuilder class provides access to values in the `<appSettings>` section of the Web.config file.
trans-unit.target: Klassen AppSettingsExpressionBuilder gir tilgang til verdiene i den `<appSettings>` -delen i Web.config-filen.

trans-unit.source: The `<appSettings>` section of the Web.config file contains application-specific values in key/value pairs.
trans-unit.target: Den `<appSettings>` -delen i Web.config-filen inneholder programspesifikk verdiene i nøkkel/verdi-par.

trans-unit.source: An application value is retrieved by assigning an expression of the form `<%$ AppSettings: appSettingsKey %>` to a property in a control declaration.
trans-unit.target: En verdi for applikasjonen som hentes ved å tilordne et uttrykk med formatet `<%$ AppSettings: appSettingsKey %>` til en egenskap i en kontroll-deklarasjon.

trans-unit.source: The part of the expression before the colon (:) designates the type of expression to be retrieved, and the part after the colon signifies the key.
trans-unit.target: En del av uttrykket før kolon (:) angir uttrykket som skal hentes og del etter kolon betyr nøkkelen.

trans-unit.source: The preceding expression would retrieve the following value from the Web.config file.
trans-unit.target: Foregående uttrykket vil hente følgende verdi fra filen Web.config.

trans-unit.source: `<appSettings>` `<add key="appSettingsKey" value="appSettingsValue"/>` `</appSettings>` When the page parser encounters an expression with the `AppSettings` prefix, it creates an instance of the AppSettingsExpressionBuilder class to handle the expression.
trans-unit.target: `<appSettings>` `<add key="appSettingsKey" value="appSettingsValue"/>` `</appSettings>`Når siden parseren støter på et uttrykk med den `AppSettings` prefiks, opprettes en forekomst av klassen AppSettingsExpressionBuilder til å håndtere uttrykket.

trans-unit.source: If the expression is encountered in a page that will be compiled, the AppSettingsExpressionBuilder object generates code to retrieve the specified value from the Web.config file.
trans-unit.target: Hvis uttrykket i en side som skal kompileres, genererer AppSettingsExpressionBuilder objektet kode for å hente den angitte verdien fra filen Web.config.

trans-unit.source: This code is executed during the execution of the generated page class.
trans-unit.target: Denne koden utføres under kjøring av klassen genererte siden.

trans-unit.source: If the expression is encountered in a page that will not be compiled, the AppSettingsExpressionBuilder object returns the value from the Web.config file when the page is parsed and executed.
trans-unit.target: Hvis uttrykket i en side som ikke skal kompileres, returnerer AppSettingsExpressionBuilder objektet verdien fra filen Web.config når siden er analysert, og kjøres.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.AppSettingsExpressionBuilder"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.AppSettingsExpressionBuilder"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value from the <xref uid="langword_csharp_<appSettings>" name="<appSettings>" href=""></xref> section of the Web.config file.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en verdi fra den <xref uid="langword_csharp_<appSettings>" name="<appSettings>" href=""> </xref> -delen i Web.config-filen.

trans-unit.source: This method is called when an expression of the form `<%$ AppSettings: someApplicationSetting %>` is encountered in a no-compile page.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles når et uttrykk med formatet `<%$ AppSettings: someApplicationSetting %>` oppstår i et Nei kompilering.

trans-unit.source: It retrieves the appropriate value from the key/value pairs in the `<appSettings>` section of the Web.config file.
trans-unit.target: Den henter riktig verdi fra nøkkel/verdi-par i den `<appSettings>` -delen i Web.config-filen.

trans-unit.source: This method overrides <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ExpressionBuilder.EvaluateExpression%2A> by calling the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.AppSettingsExpressionBuilder.GetAppSetting%2A> method with the <xref:System.Web.UI.BoundPropertyEntry.Expression%2A> property as the `key` parameter, the <xref:System.Web.UI.PropertyEntry.Name%2A> property on the <xref:System.Web.UI.PropertyEntry.PropertyInfo%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property as the `propertyName` parameter, and the <xref:System.Type> of the `target` parameter as the `targetType` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden overstyrer <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ExpressionBuilder.EvaluateExpression%2A>ved å kalle den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.AppSettingsExpressionBuilder.GetAppSetting%2A>metoden med den <xref:System.Web.UI.BoundPropertyEntry.Expression%2A>egenskapen som den `key` parameteren den <xref:System.Web.UI.PropertyEntry.Name%2A>egenskap i den <xref:System.Web.UI.PropertyEntry.PropertyInfo%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen som den `propertyName` parameteren og <xref:System.Type>for den `target` -parameteren som den `targetType` parameteren.</xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Web.UI.PropertyEntry.PropertyInfo%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.PropertyEntry.Name%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.BoundPropertyEntry.Expression%2A> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.AppSettingsExpressionBuilder.GetAppSetting%2A> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.ExpressionBuilder.EvaluateExpression%2A>

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether an expression can be evaluated in a page that is not compiled.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en verdi som angir om et uttrykk kan evalueres på en side som ikke er kompilert.

trans-unit.source: The SupportsEvaluate property indicates whether the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.AppSettingsExpressionBuilder.EvaluateExpression%2A> method has been implemented in the class and can return a value for the expression.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen SupportsEvaluate angir om den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.AppSettingsExpressionBuilder.EvaluateExpression%2A>metoden er implementert i klassen og kan returnere en verdi for uttrykket.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.AppSettingsExpressionBuilder.EvaluateExpression%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.Compilation.AppSettingsExpressionBuilder.EvaluateExpression%2A> must be implemented within an expression builder for an expression to be evaluated in a page that is not compiled.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Compilation.AppSettingsExpressionBuilder.EvaluateExpression%2A>må være implementert i expression-verktøy for et uttrykk som skal evalueres i en side som ikke er kompilert.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.AppSettingsExpressionBuilder.EvaluateExpression%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Compilation.AppSettingsExpressionBuilder> class supports evaluation of an application setting in a page that is not compiled, so it always returns `true`.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Compilation.AppSettingsExpressionBuilder>klassen støtter evalueringen av en applikasjonsinnstilling i en side som ikke er kompilert, slik at den returnerer alltid `true`.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.AppSettingsExpressionBuilder>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> in all cases.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>i alle tilfeller.
